headline: Corrections & Amplifications
summary: Laura Edwards-Leeper co-founded the nation’s first pediatric gender clinic.  A Review article on Saturday about Planned Parenthood incorrectly stated it was the first gender clinic.  FedEx said it conducted an internal investigation into a personnel issue within its information-technology organization. A Business & Finance headline and article in some editions Friday incorrectly said the company and people familiar with the matter said a unit within the IT organization,  FedEx  Dataworks, was the target of the internal investigation.
